Welcome to ARC Solver

ARC (Abstraction and Reasoning Corpus) is a puzzle game where you need to understand the pattern from training examples and apply it to solve new cases.

How to Play:

  • 1. Study the training examples to understand the pattern (Input → Output transformation)
  • 2. Use the color palette and tools to create your solution for the test input
  • 3. You have 2 attempts per puzzle. After that, it will move to the next one

Available Tools:

  • Copy Input - Start with the test input grid
  • Fill Tool - Fill connected areas of the same color
  • Paint - Click and drag to paint cells

By using this solver, you agree to the anonymous collection of your puzzle-solving data for scientific research purposes. No personal information will be stored.
